---
title: Oven-Roasted Mediterranean Pork Kebabs with Lemony Feta Rice
description: These deeply flavourful pork kebabs are slathered in tzatziki sauce and nestled on a bed of zesty, feta-tossed rice. Paired with a bright fresh salad, it's a lovely Mediterranean plate!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/kebabs-de-porc-a-la-mediterraneenne-rotis-au-four-9f5df239.jpg
